{"type": "article", "id": 4659, "title": "Phase One 全新 A-Series 中画幅相机系统", "description": "", "date": "2014-12-24T07:32:50Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 0, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160605233441N8oYMvJsiQVT1G5Z.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t丹麦顶级相机品牌 Phase One 最近发布了全新 A-Series 中画幅相机系统，该系列有 3 款机型，均是在品牌 ALPA 12TC 无反机身的基础上设计而成，A280 款采用 IQ280 机背，支持 8000 万像素，其余两款 A260 与 A250 分别达到 6000 万与 5000 万像素。3 款相机都和 ALPA HR Alpar 4.0/35mm 镜头一同发售。此外，每一款相机的机背上还设有手机夹，方便用户利用 iPhone 或 iPad 作为无线 LiveView 取景器。定价 47000－55000 美元不等，<a href=\"http://www.phaseone.com/en/FooterMenu/Partner-Locator.aspx\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<div>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/201606052334394kcTQVOfEqlvuw0z.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233439HQ5d6aXOZVnGUT9N.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605233440sWj25SZmfRbwvTrd.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}